<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idc00f6b33-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s16355"><num value="16355">§ 16355.</num><heading> National Laboratory designation</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">After <date date="2005-08-08">August 8, 2005</date>, the Secretary shall not designate a facility that is not listed in <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s15801/3">section 15801(3) of this title</ref> as a National Laboratory.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idc00f6b34-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/109/58/tIX/s991">Pub. L. 109–58, title IX, § 991</ref>, <date date="2005-08-08">Aug. 8, 2005</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/119/913">119 Stat. 913</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
